        {
            "id": 6141723,
            "title": "〈台股開盤〉台積電帶動漲逾200點穩步攻高 高價股閃現25千金",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美就業市場疲軟，市場押注 Fed 降息，美股收漲，激勵台股今 (5) 日在早盤漲逾 200 點，重返 24400 點之上，早盤估量 4400 億元，約持平昨日，而今日高價股表現亮眼，早盤更出現 25 千金。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6141723/l/05479614b41f67227d37a82c96296366.jpg\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">〈台股開盤〉台積電帶動漲逾200點穩步攻高 高價股閃現25千金 。(鉅亨網資料照)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>博通 (Broadcom)(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:AVGO:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/AVGO\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">AVGO-US</a>) 第 3 季獲利優於預期，對第 4 季財測也樂觀，並宣布客製化晶片已從新客戶手中獲得價值 100 億美元訂單，盤後大漲逾 4%；激勵博通概念股智邦、眾達 - KY 早盤股價上漲逾 3%，帶動網通類股股漲幅逾 1% 。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>早盤傳出美國總統川普又喊話「相當可觀的半導體關稅很快就來了，但在美設廠的廠商可獲豁免」，帶動台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>) 開盤 1175 元、上漲 15 元或 1.3%，聯發科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>) 也漲逾 1%，鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>) 小漲，台達電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2308:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2308\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2308-TW</a>) 大漲逾 4%，不過，聯電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2303-TW</a>)8 月營收呈現月、年均減，早盤跌逾 2%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>高價股方面，智邦 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2345:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2345\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2345-TW</a>)、台光電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2383:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2383\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2383-TW</a>)、光聖 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6442:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6442\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6442-TW</a>) 漲逾 4%，均重返千金行列，也讓早盤出現 25 千金，此外，旺矽 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6223:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6223\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6223-TW</a>)、精測 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6510:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6510\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6510-TW</a>)、AES-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6781:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6781\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6781-TW</a>) 等均亮燈漲停，高價股表現亮眼。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>宏碁 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2353:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2353\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2353-TW</a>) 持續受惠與輝達 (NVIDIA)(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:NVDA:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/NVDA\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">NVDA-US</a>) 合作超級小電腦題材，延續昨日漲停攻勢，今日再漲半根停板；非電族群方面，康霈 *(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6919:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6919\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6919-TW</a>) 表現較為強勢，漲逾 3%，華新 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1605:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1605\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1605-TW</a>) 漲多拉回、跌逾 6%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
